name: By A Thread
description:
A dew covered spidersilk thread stretches between unopened Lilac florets. The Lilac is a symbol of early growth, renewal, confidence, first love, magic and the transition from innocence to wisdom. (Syringa vulgaris)

2018. Nikon D60, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing.

1024x685 300dpi jpeg
